16:18.578 --> 16:21.612
Okay.

16:21.614 --> 16:22.780
So, that's what's wrong.

16:22.782 --> 16:24.282
♪♪

16:24.284 --> 16:28.019
I can't go back there.
I can't.

16:28.021 --> 16:29.988
