16:41.600 --> 16:44.168
[ Sobbing continues ]

16:46.605 --> 16:48.906
♪♪

17:12.798 --> 17:15.400
[ Bell dings ]

17:29.581 --> 17:31.816
Where are you going?

17:31.818 --> 17:33.384
Throwing away the food.

17:38.924 --> 17:40.691
