17:40.693 --> 17:42.827
To pee.

17:42.829 --> 17:45.329
Is that okay?
- No.

17:45.331 --> 17:47.498
Last time I let you
use the bathroom
at a gas station,

17:47.500 --> 17:49.000
you tried to jump
out the window.

17:49.002 --> 17:50.835
Then you don't trust me.

17:50.837 --> 17:52.503
I don't.

17:52.505 --> 17:55.006
Then how about you let me
go pee all by myself,

17:55.008 --> 17:56.574
and when I come
right back here,

17:56.576 --> 17:58.910
you can trust me
a little bit more?
Get in the car.

17:58.912 --> 18:01.646
If I get in the car,
I will pee on the seat.

18:05.851 --> 18:08.152
It's by the left light
at the back.

18:11.690 --> 18:14.158
[ Doorbell jingles ]

18:16.962 --> 18:19.297
Man:
You need a key.

18:21.033 --> 18:23.000
For the bathroom.

18:24.903 --> 18:26.971
Thanks.

18:31.143 --> 18:33.578
How much weed do you have?

18:33.580 --> 18:36.147
[ Massive Attack's
"Dissolved Girl" plays ]

18:40.452 --> 18:43.654
[ Console beeps ]

18:48.627 --> 18:52.497
[ Console beeps ]

18:53.899 --> 18:56.601
♪ Shame ♪

18:56.603 --> 19:00.638
♪ Such a shame ♪

19:00.640 --> 19:05.710
